; Coverage test for xact.cc throw balance_error
; An unbalanced transaction triggers "Transaction does not balance"
2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-5.00

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 5:
While balancing transaction from "$FILE", lines 3-5:
> 2024/01/01 Test
>     Expenses:Food    $10.00
>     Assets:Cash      $-5.00
Unbalanced remainder is:
               $5.00
Amount to balance against:
              $10.00
Error: Transaction does not balance
end test
